translated: Åberg, Ragnar, District Medical Officer, To-rup, b. 22/12/94 in Skönnerud, Värml. 1st, son of District Physician Jacob Gustaf Alarik A. and Anna Sofia Kristina Larsson. Married 30 with Harriet Bråkenhielm. Children: Lars Bertil and Inga Margareta, b. 31. - Passed the student exam in Luleå in 14, received a Bachelor of Medicine in Uppsala in 19, obtained a medical license in Stockholm in 23. Temporary District Medical Officer in the Fränsta district for four months from 22 to 23, assistant physician and temporary deputy senior physician in the surgical department of Sundsvalls hospital in 24, practicing physician in Ange from 24 to 31, railway physician from 26 to 31, in Kiruna from 31, permanent District Medical Officer in the Kiruna district the same year, temporary deputy physician at Sandträsk sanatorium for two months in 33, District Medical Officer in the Torup district from 40. In Kiruna, among other things, chairman of the health board, member of the child welfare board and health board in Jukkasjärvi.
